title: Slight glitch, but worth the reinstall effort
text: Slight glitch, but worth the reinstall effort The update killed this LWP on my SG4 (running 4.2). After complaining, I uninstalled, then reinstalled-fixing all issues. I LOVE this LWP!

title: Really great
text: Really great This takes the default 'phase' live wallpaper to the next level. It looks amazing on my HTC One M8. May suck a little battery, but not terrible. Highly recommended!

title: The best!
text: The best! This is my absolute favorite live wallpaper on the app store.  Believe me I have been searching for months for a great live wallpaper and this is no question the best one that I could find,  Thx for the wallpaper.

title: Ads, ads, and more ads!
text: Ads, ads, and more ads! My goodness, if you want me to purchase the pro version, then make it so I want the app.  Every single screen on the app pops up a new ad asking me to install more apps, every single time.  Maybe learn a little and realize that consumers don't want to be pestered with your popup ads.  I'm all for devs getting paid, but there are many successful devs out there that don't resort to annoying popup ads.  It's like I'm using Internet Explorer 6.  Terrible.

title: Favourite live wallpaper !!
text: Favourite live wallpaper !! This app is undoubtedly my favourite live-wallpaper app. The day I installed this, I had been using it since then, never parted with it. Sucks the minimum amount of resource compared to other live wallpapers out there. Just hope you guys add some more colours or maybe patterns on your future updates, otherwise excellent and you deserve 5 stars.

title: My favorite
text: My favorite My favorite of all the live wallpapers I've tried.  Good. locking and soothing. Get it, you'll love it too.  5 stars.:

title: Best ever

title: Liked free but uninstalled pro
text: Liked free but uninstalled pro I used the free version for a few days, no problems, liked it. Upgraded to pro and there was a huge battery drain. Plugged in to charger, my battery level was going DOWN. Uninstalled and restarted and battery now fine. Shame as liked this, but rendered phone unusable. HTC One V ICS

title: Good until ads showed uo
text: Good until ads showed uo I found this to be a great app until ads started to show up on my home screen. I realize that it is a free app, but I find the ads annoying. Was a great app before, no performance issues.
